{"tid":1499342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幫手推！！！】國際文宣新方向！！！","createTime":"2019-08-23T16:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T20:50:20.000Z","uid":93536,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"52915257a4dfc11ed4a882f64ef0b917f0809690","tid":1499342,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"國際性文宣戰既重要性毋庸置疑！但有一個方向好似大家未做過！可以一齊討論下！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就係利用外國既明星效應</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以下個人經歷，當初知道蘇丹革命，並唔係睇新聞，而係從我兩位女神<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Bella Hadid</span></strong></span>同<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Gigi Hadid</span></strong></span>既Instagram Story得知！之後發現仲有好多外國明星，講緊有幾百萬幾千萬Followers既大粒野都有Post Sudan Crisis。<span style=\"color: red;\">即係只要佢地一Post，好多外地唔關心政治唔睇新聞既<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">外地豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>都可以接收到呢啲資訊！</span>可以參考下下面條Link，Ne-Yo同Rihanna都有Post！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/mashable.com/article/sudan-crisis-no-internet-influencer-posts.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fmashable.com%2Farticle%2Fsudan-crisis-no-internet-influencer-posts.amp&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6hZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=d506a77f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/mashable.com/article/sudan-crisis-no-internet-influencer-posts.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n所以今日諗諗下，既然中共迫班奶共藝人做護旗手，點解我地唔可以向外國藝人求助？<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地係國際性社交媒體既Reach絕對比班奶共狗大！如果成功，一定好大迴響！</span>以下係我諗到既行動要點。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 轟炸式DM外國娛樂圈，講香港人道危機<span style=\"color: red;\">希望佢地會為我地發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VdXpCjr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVdXpCjr.png&h=af40d350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 推埋Eye4HK呢個Challenge出去，<span style=\"color: red;\">希望可以籍住班明星帶個浪潮去外國</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MA4SMhe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMA4SMhe.png&h=5cfcc46f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">記住要集中講<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人道危機</span></span>同今日單<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">欺壓女權事件</span></span>，你走去叫佢地幫你光復香港同打共產黨真係揾鬼理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n但得我一個Send，女神係唔撚會理架。所以希望各路手足，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果覺得呢招有用就一齊瘋狂轟炸你地既外國偶像啦。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">荷里活救港大行動，正式開始！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"908bb36789c4efe115a2267aa6cba14550e612da","tid":1499342,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:25:10.000Z","msg":"自推十連發開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5fab4dfa213d16bd46ee21785daa626f84874ec","tid":1499342,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abb2a77aa6b497d5c02bc0762033a866a8455b9","tid":1499342,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:25:30.000Z","msg":"推兩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0e8dcd28fa0ddc6146606821c859221d381b27","tid":1499342,"uid":269256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:25:31.000Z","msg":"我都send過<br />\n但冇如何回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82de931b629c9aae48a0c74e5397ae1093cd96cb","tid":1499342,"u